WEBVTT

01:52.229 --> 01:53.430
I just saw

01:53.430 --> 01:54.870
a figure flash by.

02:03.430 --> 02:04.870
There's nothing here.

02:05.760 --> 02:06.640
Commander,

02:07.000 --> 02:08.600
you must have got that wrong.

02:13.240 --> 02:14.470
If you don't trust me,

02:15.080 --> 02:17.079
you can come and check for yourself.

02:18.960 --> 02:21.090
Now that Lord Fei has already checked,

02:21.150 --> 02:22.880
there's no need to check again.

02:23.190 --> 02:24.680
Let's patrol elsewhere.

02:24.840 --> 02:26.300
Thanks for your hard work.

02:28.630 --> 02:29.430
Well,

02:31.240 --> 02:32.030
Lord Fei,

02:32.960 --> 02:33.590
it's so late.

02:33.590 --> 02:35.320
Why are you still in the palace?

02:36.120 --> 02:37.380
Don't even mention it.

02:37.560 --> 02:39.630
Although the marriage ceremony is over,

02:39.630 --> 02:41.150
Consort Ling's consummation

02:41.150 --> 02:43.000
is also part of the royal etiquette.

02:43.000 --> 02:44.630
As long as it's related to etiquette,

02:44.630 --> 02:46.800
I, the newly appointed Minister of Rites,

02:46.800 --> 02:48.150
have to supervise it personally.

02:48.150 --> 02:49.350
It's so troublesome.

02:50.360 --> 02:52.620
Then, why are you in the Imperial Garden?

02:52.680 --> 02:53.810
Didn't you know that

02:54.470 --> 02:56.930
Lord Zhang also
entered the palace tonight?

02:57.000 --> 02:58.800
His Majesty needs to
discuss something with him.

02:58.800 --> 03:01.680
So, he asked me to wait for him here.

03:02.190 --> 03:03.750
What Lord Fei says makes sense.

03:03.750 --> 03:05.190
You've worked hard.

03:05.190 --> 03:07.080
We will patrol with greater caution

03:07.080 --> 03:08.150
to protect His Majesty

03:08.150 --> 03:09.560
Lord Zhang, and you.

03:10.000 --> 03:10.840
Thank you.

03:13.080 --> 03:13.710
Let's go.

03:26.000 --> 03:27.630
The palace is heavily guarded.

03:27.630 --> 03:28.470
If you barge in like this,

03:28.470 --> 03:30.150
you might get caught.

03:30.280 --> 03:31.240
So what?

03:31.590 --> 03:34.150
I can deal with them myself.

03:34.870 --> 03:36.280
If someone is killed in the palace,

03:36.280 --> 03:38.240
security measures will be tightened.

03:38.240 --> 03:39.750
At that time, it will be

03:39.750 --> 03:41.560
more difficult for you to take action.

03:41.560 --> 03:43.079
If you have any other tasks coming up,

03:43.079 --> 03:44.210
you can just tell me.

03:44.360 --> 03:45.710
Maybe I can help.

03:46.240 --> 03:48.370
I've explored the palace pretty well.

03:48.870 --> 03:49.630
But

03:49.870 --> 03:51.240
I need the defense maps of
the Tianlang Pass

03:51.240 --> 03:52.680
and the capital.

03:53.030 --> 03:54.430
I'll have to trouble Lord Fei for that.

03:54.430 --> 03:57.430
The defense maps of
the Tianlang Pass and the capital?

03:58.280 --> 04:00.240
Do you think a civil official like me

04:00.240 --> 04:02.370
can get hold of such military secrets?

04:03.080 --> 04:04.190
Even if I can,

04:05.030 --> 04:07.080
how can you send them back to Changmo?

04:07.080 --> 04:08.520
After the grand ceremony,

04:08.520 --> 04:10.840
the envoy for the marriage alliance
will arrive in the capital,

04:10.840 --> 04:12.700
and the Hall Master will come too.

04:13.680 --> 04:15.080
The Hall Master is coming in person?

04:15.080 --> 04:15.610
Alright.

04:15.840 --> 04:16.570
I'm leaving.

04:16.630 --> 04:18.630
Remember to get me the defense maps.

04:31.390 --> 04:32.560
Jin Xi,

04:35.680 --> 04:36.810
you can leave first.

04:37.000 --> 04:38.120
I will serve Her Highness.

04:38.120 --> 04:38.800
Yes.

04:42.870 --> 04:45.480
You slept alone last night?

04:46.270 --> 04:49.070
Yesterday, Liu Chu was
called away by Lord Zhang,

04:49.750 --> 04:51.000
and didn't come back.

04:51.680 --> 04:53.190
I fell asleep by myself.

04:54.600 --> 04:56.000
On the first night of the wedding,

04:56.000 --> 04:56.530
he didn't

04:57.159 --> 04:59.090
consummate the marriage with you?

05:04.270 --> 05:06.160
Greetings, Your Highness.

05:07.560 --> 05:09.430
Greetings, Your Highness.

05:09.560 --> 05:11.000
Before His Majesty went to court,

05:11.000 --> 05:11.870
he specifically ordered me

05:11.870 --> 05:14.160
to come and see

05:14.160 --> 05:16.000
how you slept.

05:16.830 --> 05:19.070
These were also

05:19.070 --> 05:20.600
ordered by His Majesty last night

05:20.600 --> 05:21.680
in the Imperial Study.

05:21.680 --> 05:22.390
See.

05:22.510 --> 05:25.040
I brought it to you
first thing in the morning.

05:25.630 --> 05:26.800
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

05:27.270 --> 05:29.630
Then, when will His Majesty come?

05:30.120 --> 05:30.830
Well,

05:30.830 --> 05:32.159
I don't know.

05:32.240 --> 05:33.240
But I believe

05:33.240 --> 05:34.480
after His Majesty finishes court,

05:34.480 --> 05:35.800
he will come to see you.

05:36.630 --> 05:38.920
I shall take my leave now.

05:38.920 --> 05:39.450
Alright.

05:50.830 --> 05:51.600
General Xiao.

05:51.600 --> 05:52.270
Lord Fei.

05:52.800 --> 05:55.270
After days of comparison and analysis,

05:55.390 --> 05:56.950
we found the plague in Huangpi Village

05:56.950 --> 05:58.430
indeed bears a striking resemblance

05:58.430 --> 06:00.240
to the great plague eight years ago.

06:00.240 --> 06:01.440
They are just similar

06:01.480 --> 06:02.630
but not the same?

06:02.630 --> 06:03.240
No.

06:03.830 --> 06:04.510
Although this disease

06:04.510 --> 06:05.800
is very similar to

06:05.800 --> 06:06.800
the great plague eight years ago,

06:06.800 --> 06:08.510
we still found some

06:08.510 --> 06:09.710
subtle differences.

06:09.750 --> 06:12.480
Please look at the examination report,
My Lords.

06:13.600 --> 06:14.870
An unknown toxin was found

06:14.870 --> 06:16.800
in this plague.

06:17.480 --> 06:18.680
I haven't found out

06:18.750 --> 06:20.040
what exactly the poison is yet.

06:20.040 --> 06:20.630
Poison?

06:21.430 --> 06:22.120
Yes.

06:22.720 --> 06:23.680
That is to say,

06:23.750 --> 06:24.950
this epidemic

06:25.120 --> 06:26.240
is not a natural disaster.

06:26.240 --> 06:27.570
Not a natural disaster?

06:28.070 --> 06:29.270
Could it be man-made?

06:30.270 --> 06:32.480
You mean someone spread the poison?

06:32.480 --> 06:33.750
We will find

06:33.750 --> 06:35.159
the source of the ash as soon as possible

06:35.159 --> 06:37.090
to help Lord Fei uncover the truth.

06:37.270 --> 06:38.600
Thank you for your help.

06:43.920 --> 06:44.950
Jin Xi.

06:45.480 --> 06:47.000
It's so late.

06:47.390 --> 06:49.390
Do you think Liu Chu is still coming?

06:52.480 --> 06:55.560
No emperor visits a concubine's palace
every day.

06:56.190 --> 06:57.250
If he doesn't come,

06:57.270 --> 06:58.750
we'll just rest early.

07:00.950 --> 07:01.750
Alright.

07:02.480 --> 07:03.680
I'm sleepy anyway.

07:10.190 --> 07:11.430
Greetings, Your Majesty.

07:11.430 --> 07:13.690
Your Majesty, it's so late. You still...

07:14.830 --> 07:16.830
I was just discussing with
Zhang Ruizhong and Li Shichang

07:16.830 --> 07:19.070
about the expansion of the army
in the capital.

07:19.070 --> 07:20.930
I came to you as soon as I finished.

07:21.870 --> 07:22.730
Your Highness,

07:23.070 --> 07:24.870
I'd better wait for you outside.

07:24.870 --> 07:26.470
Call me if you need anything.

07:33.360 --> 07:34.750
Who is this?

07:35.800 --> 07:36.920
That's Jin Xi.

07:36.920 --> 07:38.480
She accompanied me from Changmo

07:38.480 --> 07:39.680
as my personal female official.

07:39.680 --> 07:40.830
We grew up together.

07:43.390 --> 07:46.070
For a moment just now,

07:48.070 --> 07:50.430
I felt like I had seen that look of hers

07:50.720 --> 07:51.780
somewhere before.

07:52.680 --> 07:53.310
You're familiar with her gaze?

07:53.310 --> 07:53.950
Yeah.

07:54.240 --> 07:55.480
It seems like

07:55.680 --> 07:58.210
when Fei Zheng
entered the Prince's Mansion.

07:58.480 --> 08:00.000
What are you talking about?

08:00.000 --> 08:01.390
Lord Fei is a man.

08:01.680 --> 08:02.800
Jin Xi is a girl.

08:02.800 --> 08:03.830
How can they be the same?

08:03.830 --> 08:05.430
Really, I'm not lying to you.

08:07.630 --> 08:08.230
Forget it.

08:08.430 --> 08:09.560
It's not important.

08:11.000 --> 08:11.830
Tonight,

08:12.310 --> 08:13.950
I will stay here with you.

08:15.600 --> 08:16.240
Really?

08:16.240 --> 08:17.160
Of course it is.

08:17.160 --> 08:18.390
When have I ever lied to you?

08:18.390 --> 08:18.830
Right?

08:21.600 --> 08:22.680
Your Majesty.

08:24.070 --> 08:25.680
Your Majesty.

08:26.390 --> 08:27.800
Damn Lord Zhang.

08:31.600 --> 08:32.480
I

08:33.549 --> 08:34.750
will be right back.

08:35.840 --> 08:38.299
You didn't come back
last time you said that.

08:41.840 --> 08:42.909
I swear.

08:43.200 --> 08:44.400
This is the last time.

08:44.440 --> 08:45.480
It won't happen again.

08:45.480 --> 08:46.080
All right.

08:46.510 --> 08:47.030
Yeah.

08:47.550 --> 08:48.200
Okay.

08:48.440 --> 08:49.150
Then,

08:49.240 --> 08:49.970
I am leaving.

08:50.240 --> 08:50.750
Okay.

09:00.840 --> 09:01.480
Your Majesty.

09:01.480 --> 09:02.200
Lord Zhang.

09:02.480 --> 09:03.200
Okay.

09:03.240 --> 09:03.910
Lord Zhang,

09:04.390 --> 09:06.670
today isn't any special occasion.

09:07.150 --> 09:08.000
Besides,

09:08.360 --> 09:09.480
with so much wine,

09:09.480 --> 09:11.140
how can the two of us finish it?

09:11.630 --> 09:13.630
You may not know this, Your Majesty.

09:13.670 --> 09:16.440
Today is the anniversary of

09:16.440 --> 09:19.870
my first military campaign
with the late Emperor.

09:20.150 --> 09:22.840
Don't you think we should celebrate?

09:23.080 --> 09:24.280
Of course, we should.

09:24.670 --> 09:25.550
Lord Zhang,

09:25.870 --> 09:28.480
without the battles you
and the late Emperor fought,

09:28.480 --> 09:30.360
Jinglan wouldn't be what it is today.

09:30.360 --> 09:30.870
Yes.

09:30.870 --> 09:32.670
Come on. Let me offer you a toast,
Lord Zhang.

09:32.670 --> 09:33.750
To Your Majesty.

09:34.270 --> 09:34.870
Cheers.

09:43.670 --> 09:44.480
He

09:44.910 --> 09:45.960
left again.

09:46.840 --> 09:48.360
He said he would come back.

09:50.240 --> 09:51.270
I highly doubt it.

09:51.840 --> 09:53.630
I saw Lord Zhang at the door earlier

09:53.630 --> 09:54.750
with a lot of wine.

09:55.240 --> 09:57.240
I don't know what he's up to tonight.

09:59.030 --> 10:00.490
I will wait for him anyway.

10:01.480 --> 10:02.150
Alright.

10:02.720 --> 10:04.180
Then, I'll accompany you.

10:16.670 --> 10:17.150
Come on.

10:17.480 --> 10:19.280
Let me fill your cup, Lord Zhang.

10:21.270 --> 10:22.510
Back then,

10:22.910 --> 10:24.480
I followed the late Emperor

10:24.480 --> 10:27.790
and fought our way
through the battlefields.

10:28.000 --> 10:29.720
I deeply understand

10:29.720 --> 10:32.000
how hard-won this empire is.

10:34.750 --> 10:36.880
The late Emperor passed away suddenly

10:37.270 --> 10:39.400
and asked me to be your Chief Minister.

10:42.600 --> 10:44.440
Actually, Your Majesty,

10:44.670 --> 10:46.600
at my age,

10:46.600 --> 10:48.440
I should have retired long ago

10:48.440 --> 10:49.670
and enjoyed my twilight years.

10:49.670 --> 10:51.750
To be honest,

10:51.910 --> 10:55.150
I should have lived a carefree
life with my grandchildren.

10:55.150 --> 10:57.240
Really, Lord Zhang?

10:57.240 --> 10:58.170
With this glass,

10:58.670 --> 11:00.120
I wish you

11:00.390 --> 11:02.320
many children and grandchildren.

11:03.360 --> 11:04.760
Thank you, Your Majesty.

11:05.150 --> 11:06.080
After you, Lord Zhang.

11:06.080 --> 11:06.750
Please.

11:06.750 --> 11:07.840
Your Majesty.

11:11.030 --> 11:13.490
You can really hold your liquor,
Lord Zhang.

11:16.600 --> 11:17.550
Your Majesty,

11:18.360 --> 11:20.200
I am truly not clinging to

11:20.200 --> 11:22.630
the position of Chief Minister.

11:23.240 --> 11:26.840
I just worry about you, Your Majesty.

11:27.600 --> 11:29.120
I also worry about

11:29.120 --> 11:31.150
Jinglan's land

11:31.360 --> 11:32.030
Lord Zhang.

11:32.030 --> 11:33.240
and its people.

11:33.480 --> 11:35.390
I cannot do it without you.

11:35.480 --> 11:36.390
Jinglan

11:36.630 --> 11:38.080
needs you even more.

11:38.080 --> 11:39.150
Lord Zhang.

11:39.150 --> 11:40.810
You flatter me, Your Majesty.

11:41.270 --> 11:43.320
You flatter me, Your Majesty.

11:43.320 --> 11:43.960
Come on.

11:51.870 --> 11:52.790
Your Majesty,

11:53.360 --> 11:55.030
I invited you out tonight

11:55.270 --> 11:57.600
not only to commemorate the late Emperor,

11:57.670 --> 12:00.120
but also because I don't want you

12:00.120 --> 12:03.030
to lose yourself
in Consort Ling's tenderness

12:03.150 --> 12:06.080
and be unable to extricate yourself.

12:07.670 --> 12:08.670
Rest assured.

12:09.440 --> 12:11.120
I will definitely be

12:11.600 --> 12:14.750
a wise ruler who knows
how to judge and use people.

12:15.440 --> 12:17.030
Good, Your Majesty.

12:20.030 --> 12:23.360
Remember to cherish this hard-won empire

12:23.440 --> 12:25.440
and the people of Jinglan.

12:26.360 --> 12:27.600
I believe

12:27.910 --> 12:30.510
you will certainly be
a wise and just emperor.

12:30.870 --> 12:31.600
To Your Majesty.

12:31.600 --> 12:32.630
Then, with this cup,

12:32.630 --> 12:34.600
we toast to the land of Jinglan,

12:34.750 --> 12:36.240
and to the future of Jinglan.

12:36.240 --> 12:37.120
Lord Zhang.

12:38.150 --> 12:39.030
Please.

13:01.000 --> 13:02.080
Your Majesty.

13:06.480 --> 13:07.670
Your Majesty.

13:09.480 --> 13:11.150
It is all for Jinglan.

13:32.750 --> 13:34.670
Judging by the Your Highness's look,

13:34.670 --> 13:36.480
the treasury must be full again.

13:36.630 --> 13:38.390
The weather has been good,

13:38.390 --> 13:39.790
and the land is peaceful this year.

13:39.790 --> 13:42.200
Both the national and royal treasuries

13:42.200 --> 13:44.260
have 30% more than in previous years.

13:44.550 --> 13:46.440
This is truly worth celebrating.

13:46.840 --> 13:47.790
However,

13:47.960 --> 13:50.220
this is all thanks to you, Your Highness.

13:51.750 --> 13:53.120
I heard

13:53.120 --> 13:55.360
that His Majesty spent the most
on his royal wedding

13:55.360 --> 13:57.390
compared to all previous monarchs.

13:58.750 --> 14:00.440
I only have one brother.

14:00.480 --> 14:01.870
It's his first marriage.

14:01.870 --> 14:03.080
As his sister,

14:03.080 --> 14:04.360
how could I be stingy?

14:04.480 --> 14:06.670
You are so good to His Majesty,
Your Highness.

14:06.670 --> 14:08.360
I hope His Majesty will always keep

14:08.360 --> 14:09.890
this kindness in his heart.

14:12.390 --> 14:13.550
I heard that

14:13.550 --> 14:17.750
His Majesty and Consort Ling didn't
consummate their marriage last night.

14:18.200 --> 14:19.320
Lord Zhang

14:19.320 --> 14:20.780
is such a stubborn old man.

14:21.240 --> 14:22.270
The ceremony is only complete

14:22.270 --> 14:24.030
after the marriage is consummated.

14:24.030 --> 14:25.120
Why is he

14:25.120 --> 14:26.250
standing in the way?

14:27.480 --> 14:29.870
Should we help His Majesty out?

14:30.550 --> 14:31.390
No.

14:31.600 --> 14:32.480
It's their own business.

14:32.480 --> 14:34.010
Let nature take its course.

14:37.150 --> 14:37.750
By the way,

14:38.390 --> 14:40.390
did Consort Ling say anything?

14:40.390 --> 14:42.150
Consort Ling is fine.

14:43.080 --> 14:44.750
But Jin Xi,

14:46.080 --> 14:47.870
the female official beside her,

14:47.870 --> 14:49.330
is indeed a hidden danger.

14:50.030 --> 14:51.630
We can't let her stay in the palace.

14:51.630 --> 14:53.290
Find a chance to drive her out.

14:53.670 --> 14:55.000
Go prepare a courtyard.

14:55.870 --> 14:57.150
The palace

14:57.480 --> 14:59.480
must be clean.

15:06.550 --> 15:07.910
Don't you think

15:08.320 --> 15:09.980
Chu has something on his mind?

15:10.790 --> 15:12.440
General Xiao, you are so clever.

15:12.440 --> 15:14.170
Why don't you ask him yourself?

15:15.080 --> 15:15.790
Chu...

15:16.790 --> 15:17.790
Don't ask.

15:18.870 --> 15:19.960
I'm fine.

15:21.270 --> 15:22.120
I'm good.

15:22.870 --> 15:23.720
Chu,

15:24.030 --> 15:25.790
it seems that since the marriage alliance,

15:25.790 --> 15:27.390
you haven't been very happy.

15:28.360 --> 15:30.030
I am quite happy.

15:30.550 --> 15:33.120
Then, why do you look so exhausted?

15:36.030 --> 15:37.080
Chu,

15:37.360 --> 15:39.030
are you and Consort Ling

15:40.600 --> 15:41.790
not sleeping well?

15:42.360 --> 15:44.360
What kind of question is that?

15:45.120 --> 15:47.180
It's mostly Zhang Ruizhong's fault.

15:47.790 --> 15:48.630
Lord Zhang,

15:49.440 --> 15:50.870
that stubborn old man,

15:51.120 --> 15:52.150
every night,

15:52.150 --> 15:54.000
when Wanyu and I are together,

15:54.080 --> 15:56.480
he insists on eavesdropping at our door.

15:56.550 --> 15:58.120
He either wants to discuss

15:58.120 --> 15:59.150
national affairs with me,

15:59.150 --> 16:01.880
or wants to drink
and have a heart-to-heart talk.

16:02.670 --> 16:04.070
He is a veteran minister.

16:04.550 --> 16:06.410
It's inappropriate if I don't go.

16:06.550 --> 16:07.950
But I can't outdrink him.

16:09.480 --> 16:11.140
I really don't know what to do.

16:14.080 --> 16:14.880
General Xiao,

16:15.240 --> 16:16.960
can you tolerate this?

16:17.200 --> 16:18.360
I cannot.

16:18.550 --> 16:19.480
Lord Fei,

16:19.550 --> 16:20.670
can you?

16:20.670 --> 16:21.870
I can't either.

16:21.960 --> 16:24.550
Do you have a solution, General Xiao?

16:24.840 --> 16:26.270
That depends on what solution

16:26.270 --> 16:27.750
Lord Fei has.

16:27.750 --> 16:29.480
What are you two talking about?

16:29.750 --> 16:30.550
Chu,

16:31.440 --> 16:32.480
rest assured.

16:32.480 --> 16:35.360
Tonight, we'll let you and Consort Ling...

16:40.670 --> 16:42.000
We shall take our leave.

16:42.030 --> 16:43.160
Where are you going?

16:43.480 --> 16:44.200
Wait.

16:44.630 --> 16:45.390
Tell me.

16:45.390 --> 16:46.440
Tell me where you are going.

16:46.440 --> 16:47.570
Where are you going?

16:49.870 --> 16:50.670
Jin Xi.

16:51.510 --> 16:53.640
Did you pick all these from the palace?

16:53.670 --> 16:54.440
Yes.

16:54.840 --> 16:56.480
I took one branch from every tree,

16:56.480 --> 16:58.480
and three blooms from every flower,

16:58.600 --> 16:59.750
and got this many.

17:00.320 --> 17:01.670
You just came to the palace.

17:01.670 --> 17:03.870
Why are you so familiar with the palace?

17:05.790 --> 17:06.790
Not really.

17:08.589 --> 17:10.119
Greetings, Your Highness.

17:13.589 --> 17:14.750
Greetings, Xie.

17:15.109 --> 17:15.960
You may rise.

17:16.240 --> 17:17.880
Xie, what brings you here?

17:18.000 --> 17:19.200
I came to see you.

17:20.069 --> 17:20.790
How is it?

17:21.240 --> 17:23.700
Are you getting used to
living in the palace?

17:24.200 --> 17:25.680
I eat well in the palace,

17:25.680 --> 17:26.540
and sleep well.

17:26.880 --> 17:27.960
I am doing very well.

17:27.960 --> 17:28.720
Good？

17:30.400 --> 17:34.130
I heard you and His Mahesty
haven't consummated your marriage yet.

17:36.960 --> 17:39.640
Liu Chu has been a bit busy lately.

17:41.200 --> 17:42.550
Good things take time.

17:42.680 --> 17:44.880
You two will be together for a lifetime,

17:45.030 --> 17:46.480
so there's no rush.

17:47.000 --> 17:47.800
Rest assured.

17:47.960 --> 17:48.960
With me here,

17:49.030 --> 17:50.510
you will

17:50.510 --> 17:51.640
have a happy life.

17:56.000 --> 17:57.440
I came today

17:58.030 --> 18:00.350
mainly to talk to you about Jin Xi.

18:02.240 --> 18:03.030
Jin Xi?

18:03.480 --> 18:04.790
I heard

18:04.790 --> 18:06.960
Jin Xi is very loyal to you.

18:07.350 --> 18:09.480
She accompanied you
from Changmo to Jinglan,

18:09.480 --> 18:10.610
and into the palace.

18:11.160 --> 18:12.830
Now that you are with His Majesty,

18:12.830 --> 18:14.000
I'm thinking of

18:14.030 --> 18:15.830
finding a good home for her.

18:18.440 --> 18:19.640
Outside the palace,

18:19.640 --> 18:20.880
I have a courtyard.

18:21.000 --> 18:22.530
I plan to let her live there.

18:22.680 --> 18:23.960
And every month,

18:23.960 --> 18:27.240
I'll allocate some money from the treasury
for her living expenses.

18:27.240 --> 18:28.240
But

18:28.590 --> 18:30.440
Jin Xi and I are like sisters.

18:30.680 --> 18:31.810
If she is not here...

18:33.200 --> 18:35.070
Precisely because you are like sisters,

18:35.070 --> 18:36.480
she shouldn't stay by your side forever

18:36.480 --> 18:37.590
to serve you.

18:38.030 --> 18:39.640
She needs her own residence,

18:39.640 --> 18:40.640
her own life,

18:40.640 --> 18:41.770
and her own husband.

18:42.680 --> 18:43.880
Don't you agree?

18:49.680 --> 18:51.540
Your Highness's good intentions

18:51.640 --> 18:52.960
are surely meant well.

18:53.270 --> 18:54.590
Since you've said so,

18:54.590 --> 18:56.850
there must be no chance for negotiation.

18:56.880 --> 18:58.140
I can leave the palace.

18:58.400 --> 18:59.880
But after I leave,

19:00.880 --> 19:02.740
who can take care of Her Highness?

19:02.880 --> 19:04.270
Rest assured about that.

19:04.270 --> 19:04.920
I will arrange for

19:04.920 --> 19:07.160
more clever maids to serve you.

19:07.480 --> 19:08.440
As long as I have time,

19:08.440 --> 19:09.640
I will also come see you.

19:09.640 --> 19:10.480
Besides,

19:10.640 --> 19:12.750
you're not forbidden from
entering the palace forever.

19:12.750 --> 19:14.400
Whenever you miss Consort Ling,

19:14.400 --> 19:16.000
you can come see her anytime.

19:18.960 --> 19:19.590
Okay.

19:19.790 --> 19:21.030
Then, I am relieved.

19:22.200 --> 19:24.730
I will follow Your Highness's
arrangements.

19:26.070 --> 19:26.920
Then,

19:27.480 --> 19:28.550
it's settled?

19:30.270 --> 19:31.070
Okay.

19:48.790 --> 19:49.270
Who is it?

19:49.270 --> 19:50.470
Keep your voice down.

19:50.640 --> 19:51.840
Keep your voice down.

19:51.880 --> 19:53.240
Lord Zhang
has been looking for me all night.

19:53.240 --> 19:54.350
He's so annoying.

19:55.160 --> 19:56.880
If Lord Zhang is looking for you, just go.

19:56.880 --> 19:58.610
He has no real business with me.

19:58.640 --> 19:59.960
It's all nonsense.

20:00.240 --> 20:01.700
Or he's just lecturing me.

20:02.880 --> 20:03.880
I think

20:04.070 --> 20:06.070
he just doesn't want me to come here.

20:07.400 --> 20:09.480
But I'm not going anywhere today.

20:12.880 --> 20:16.270
Your Majesty,
I've been waiting for you for a long time.

20:16.270 --> 20:17.400
Let me deal with him.

20:17.720 --> 20:18.720
Your Majesty.

20:19.070 --> 20:20.030
Lord Zhang.

20:20.400 --> 20:21.400
Why are you here?

20:21.590 --> 20:24.750
I have something to discuss
with His Majesty.

20:28.880 --> 20:30.270
Backup is here.

20:30.270 --> 20:31.110
Lord Zhang.

20:31.310 --> 20:33.000
You brought so much good wine.

20:33.000 --> 20:35.590
General Xiao and I are just about to
have a drink together.

20:35.590 --> 20:36.200
Why don't we go together?

20:36.200 --> 20:38.550
No. No. I really have business
with His Majesty.

20:38.550 --> 20:39.400
Lord Zhang, come on.

20:39.400 --> 20:41.880
Let me tell you something interesting
about the Tianlang Pass.

20:41.880 --> 20:42.240
No.

20:42.240 --> 20:42.830
The wine...

20:42.830 --> 20:43.750
Let's go, Lord Zhang.

20:43.750 --> 20:45.200
I want to drink with His Majesty.

20:45.200 --> 20:46.240
What's the point of drinking here?

20:46.240 --> 20:47.310
Let's drink at Tianxiang Restaurant.

20:47.310 --> 20:49.570
I really have business with His Majesty.

20:52.000 --> 20:53.800
They won't come back, will they?

20:53.880 --> 20:54.880
They won't.

20:55.270 --> 20:57.350
Although Xiao Chi can't hold his drink,

20:57.350 --> 20:59.720
Fei Zheng can hold his liquor.

20:59.960 --> 21:00.550
Huh？

21:01.200 --> 21:02.000
What's up?

21:02.880 --> 21:04.110
Anyway, tonight,

21:04.440 --> 21:05.770
I'm not going anywhere.

21:06.270 --> 21:07.160
Your Majesty.

21:10.480 --> 21:11.240
Who is it?

21:11.240 --> 21:12.070
Your Majesty,

21:12.270 --> 21:14.790
Her Highness sent nuptial wine.

21:14.790 --> 21:16.350
Thank you, Xie.

21:16.350 --> 21:17.880
Can you leave it at the door?

21:32.270 --> 21:34.030
Go out and have a drink.

21:34.400 --> 21:35.590
Drink again?

21:36.750 --> 21:37.640
Drink what?

22:21.350 --> 22:22.480
Your Majesty.

22:26.400 --> 22:27.640
Your Majesty.

22:30.160 --> 22:31.270
Stop shouting.

22:32.480 --> 22:35.240
But we have to attend the morning court.

22:41.240 --> 22:42.110
Wait for me.

22:42.680 --> 22:44.740
I will accompany you after the court.

23:04.270 --> 23:06.310
His Majesty has arrived.

23:06.680 --> 23:07.480
Your Majesty.

23:08.880 --> 23:09.510
At ease.

23:09.750 --> 23:10.720
Rise.

23:12.750 --> 23:14.010
Is she still sleeping?

23:14.440 --> 23:15.030
Yes.

23:49.640 --> 23:51.440
Your Majesty, why are you here?

23:51.750 --> 23:53.480
Jin Xi, why didn't you tell me?

23:53.880 --> 23:54.940
I did it on purpose.

23:54.960 --> 23:56.640
I told them not to wake you.

23:57.270 --> 23:59.240
I just wanted to see you sleep.

23:59.640 --> 24:00.480
So cute.

24:00.480 --> 24:02.160
I haven't washed up yet.

24:03.640 --> 24:04.480
Then,

24:06.880 --> 24:08.440
get up and wash up now.

24:08.640 --> 24:09.400
Then,

24:09.790 --> 24:11.190
I'll take you somewhere.

24:11.480 --> 24:12.830
Then, wait for me.

24:13.830 --> 24:14.350
Okay.

24:14.550 --> 24:16.030
I'll wait for you outside.

24:16.830 --> 24:18.350
Sorry to keep Your Majesty waiting.

24:18.350 --> 24:19.880
Please wait for me outside.

24:20.000 --> 24:20.680
Okay.

24:29.160 --> 24:30.680
Why haven't you left yet?

24:31.030 --> 24:32.350
Hurry up and get out.

24:32.510 --> 24:33.160
Get out.

24:33.880 --> 24:35.240
I don't want to.

24:35.240 --> 24:36.550
I don't want to go out.

24:43.240 --> 24:44.570
It's daytime right now.

24:44.880 --> 24:45.790
So what?

24:46.480 --> 24:47.400
I don't care.

24:48.880 --> 24:50.790
But I need to wash up.

24:51.030 --> 24:51.830
Okay.

24:52.350 --> 24:53.550
But I think

24:54.160 --> 24:56.090
you look beautiful no matter what.

24:56.640 --> 24:58.770
Aren't you going to take me out to play?

25:01.070 --> 25:01.920
Yes.

25:02.350 --> 25:03.350
Then.

25:04.510 --> 25:06.070
I'll let you off today.

25:06.240 --> 25:07.030
Thanks.

25:07.960 --> 25:09.590
Then, I'll wait for you outside.

25:09.590 --> 25:10.160
Okay.

25:10.750 --> 25:11.880
Hurry up and wash up.

25:13.110 --> 25:13.680
I'm waiting for you.

25:13.680 --> 25:14.110
Okay.

26:06.070 --> 26:08.270
Jinglan has a vast territory.

26:08.640 --> 26:10.750
It has nine provinces
and eighteen counties.

26:10.750 --> 26:11.960
It faces the sea to the east,

26:11.960 --> 26:13.480
has grasslands to the west,

26:13.480 --> 26:15.480
and borders Mount Jing to the south.

26:15.480 --> 26:16.160
To the north

26:16.750 --> 26:17.880
is your Changmo.

26:18.590 --> 26:21.480
If Changmo and Jinglan can
maintain good relations for generations,

26:21.480 --> 26:22.720
then the whole world

26:23.200 --> 26:24.600
will be at peace forever.

26:25.590 --> 26:26.590
The King of Changmo has already sent you

26:26.590 --> 26:28.030
to Jinglan as a hostage.

26:28.440 --> 26:29.880
How could the two countries

26:29.880 --> 26:31.480
not be on good terms forever?

26:31.680 --> 26:33.080
I came here voluntarily.

26:34.550 --> 26:35.750
All right.

26:36.640 --> 26:37.350
I swear,

26:37.750 --> 26:38.880
from now on,

26:39.030 --> 26:39.750
Jinglan

26:39.750 --> 26:40.510
and Changmo

26:41.270 --> 26:42.600
will be like one family,

26:42.880 --> 26:44.350
and there will be no more wars.

26:44.350 --> 26:45.440
I will also

26:45.440 --> 26:46.960
teach our children

26:47.070 --> 26:49.240
and all the descendants of Jinglan

26:49.640 --> 26:50.960
to keep this promise.

26:52.030 --> 26:52.880
Okay.

26:59.350 --> 27:00.310
You have sent many spies

27:00.310 --> 27:01.830
in the past years.

27:02.030 --> 27:03.310
Now, your Caidie Hall

27:03.310 --> 27:05.030
is finally being useful, huh?

27:06.270 --> 27:08.790
Jinglan's national strength is
stronger than Changmo's.

27:08.790 --> 27:10.120
They have more talents.

27:10.270 --> 27:12.350
Many members of our Caidie Hall died.

27:12.350 --> 27:14.950
Finally, we managed to
plant a few spies there.

27:15.030 --> 27:16.110
General Gan,

27:16.400 --> 27:18.330
didn't you fail to defeat Xiao Chi?

27:19.240 --> 27:20.400
On the battlefield,

27:20.480 --> 27:23.160
there aren't many
who can fight me for a few rounds.

27:23.160 --> 27:24.000
Let alone

27:24.070 --> 27:25.550
fight me to a draw.

27:26.000 --> 27:28.200
As they say, heroes appreciate heroes.

27:28.440 --> 27:29.270
Besides,

27:29.480 --> 27:30.550
I didn't kill him

27:31.160 --> 27:33.030
because I wanted to play a little longer.

27:33.030 --> 27:35.070
Then, be careful, General Gan.

27:35.350 --> 27:37.480
Don't risk your life.

27:37.790 --> 27:38.270
You!

27:45.960 --> 27:47.420
Greetings, Your Majesty.

27:50.270 --> 27:52.590
This marriage alliance went smoothly.

27:53.880 --> 27:56.080
Caidie Hall made a great contribution.

27:56.400 --> 27:57.590
Thank you, Your Majesty.

27:57.590 --> 27:58.270
Rise.

28:00.680 --> 28:01.680
I'm thinking that

28:01.750 --> 28:02.510
Fei Zheng

28:02.720 --> 28:04.200
has been in Jinglan for years.

28:04.200 --> 28:05.590
It's time he made himself useful.

28:05.590 --> 28:06.200
Yes.

28:06.400 --> 28:09.000
I will go to Jinglan
with the marriage alliance envoy.

28:09.000 --> 28:11.000
I will officially activate him then.

28:11.000 --> 28:11.800
Your Majesty,

28:12.000 --> 28:13.680
we don't need to
go through all that trouble.

28:13.680 --> 28:14.920
Just attack Jinglan directly.

28:14.920 --> 28:16.070
Wouldn't that be more satisfying?

28:16.070 --> 28:18.030
Tianlang Pass is
a key stronghold of Jinglan.

28:18.030 --> 28:19.440
It is easy to defend and hard to attack.

28:19.440 --> 28:21.640
General Gan,
you only want the thrill of the kill,

28:21.640 --> 28:24.750
completely ignoring
the lives of our Changmo soldiers, huh?

28:24.750 --> 28:25.640
Using venomous insects and poison

28:25.640 --> 28:26.880
is despicable.

28:27.030 --> 28:28.240
Even if we win,

28:28.240 --> 28:29.840
it will be an unfair victory.

28:30.350 --> 28:31.270
Whatever methods are used

28:31.270 --> 28:32.350
or schemes are played,

28:32.350 --> 28:33.750
they are all reasonable.

28:34.270 --> 28:35.160
General Gan,

28:35.270 --> 28:36.480
do you think a war between two countries

28:36.480 --> 28:38.350
is just a fight between two kids?

28:38.350 --> 28:40.270
Do you know

28:40.270 --> 28:41.030
how many soldiers
will die in the flames of war?

28:41.030 --> 28:42.000
Victory

28:42.200 --> 28:43.460
is the most important.

28:47.000 --> 28:48.590
Well said, Military Advisor Modu.

28:48.590 --> 28:50.640
We must win with the lowest cost

28:50.960 --> 28:53.200
and the most secure method.

28:54.880 --> 28:56.790
Gan Yi, continue training the troops.

28:56.790 --> 28:57.590
Rest assured.

28:57.680 --> 28:59.550
There will be a time for you
to fulfill your ambitions.

28:59.550 --> 29:00.610
I accept the order.

29:01.880 --> 29:03.200
Military Advisor Modu,

29:03.200 --> 29:03.880
next time,

29:04.510 --> 29:07.750
you should go to Jinglan
with the tribute envoy.

29:07.750 --> 29:08.240
Yes.

29:09.310 --> 29:10.920
I have already prepared

29:10.920 --> 29:12.350
a surprise for Liu Chu.

29:13.440 --> 29:14.960
As for you...

29:17.030 --> 29:18.640
I know what I need to do.

29:21.160 --> 29:21.680
Good.

29:22.680 --> 29:23.590
Excellent.

29:40.880 --> 29:41.790
Liu Zheng.

29:42.480 --> 29:44.480
The day I conquer Jinglan,

29:45.200 --> 29:47.030
in front of your grave,

29:47.790 --> 29:50.480
I will kill your son, Liu Chu,

29:51.200 --> 29:53.480
to keep you company.
